{"tid":800191,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同另一半嘈黎嘈去都係因為一個原因","createTime":"2018-08-30T16:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T05:50:44.000Z","uid":149924,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9bc1f4e6bb666b68d6082c0c10611c8c8b3f4edb","tid":800191,"uid":149924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:08:30.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊左半年幾<br />\n佢要我去改變既我都全部改變左<br />\n我同佢一齊咁耐我都叫佢唔好成日食煙<br />\n但係佢就唔聽嘈交都係因為佢食煙<br />\n我已經請過我屋企人同埋我唔鍾意人食煙<br />\n咁佢仲細個學咩人食煙<br />\n佢話想見一見我屋企人我帶左佢去見<br />\n見完之後佢話佢會介左煙佢<br />\n但係一番到屋企又起個袋攞支煙出黎食<br />\n其實我日日有同佢傾過下咁<br />\n但係一講到叫佢唔好食煙又會同我嘈交<br />\n仲有可能嘈到講分手<br />\n咁我都係緊張同擔心佢身體姐<br />\n同埋佢屋企人同埋我屋企人都係好唔鍾意人地食煙既人黎<br />\n想問下大家我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩方法可以令佢唔食或者食小啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d811b1781fdb309f50536cfae9f010aa0366c75","tid":800191,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7325c5aad75cec53516ed9c45bf7b490550b8b","tid":800191,"uid":149924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:15:19.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人可以比個方法我或者屌醒我？<br />\n仲值得同佢一齊？"},{"pid":"447d0103da9ca484dcea998bd0d40cc4cdd91b6a","tid":800191,"uid":149924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d811b1781fdb309f50536cfae9f010aa0366c75","tid":800191,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"你有同樣經歷？"},{"pid":"26c52bf8ba742ce4ba8bc0ba389591c6a1277916","tid":800191,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"你當初同佢一齊嘅時候知唔知佢食煙先"},{"pid":"b73f197a2fe46ed8bdeaf85c64708df677702517","tid":800191,"uid":14992